BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 435 Td (* Receive consideration, affection, and acceptance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 413 Td (* Take pride in what I accomplish) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 391 Td (* Be treated with respect by those I care for) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 369 Td (* Make mistakes without feeling like a failure) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 347 Td (* Protect my individuality and my right to a life of my own) Tj ET
